---
// A centered callout section that matches the site's dark theme.
// Title: Let Astro AI Pick the Best Model for You
---

<section class="py-20 bg-dark">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-dark-light px-6 sm:px-10 py-14 text-center shadow-lg">
      <!-- Small logo badge -->
      <div class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/logo/spaceman.png" alt="Astro AI Logo" class="h-10 w-10 object-contain" />
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3">
        Let Astro AI Pick the Best Model for You
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <span class="font-semibold">Not sure which AI model to choose?</span>
        Choose <span class="text-primary font-medium">Auto</span> and Astro AI will automatically select the most suitable one based on your prompt.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-2">
        It keeps your conversation context intact—even when switching models—so you never lose your place.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-white/90 font-medium">
        ⚡ <span class="font-semibold">Just write what you need and Astro AI handles the rest.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
